      <div class="projects">
        <div class="projects-heading">
          <h2><span class="red-text">M</span>y Projects</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="projects-content">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-img">
              <img src="/imgs/projects/bug-tracker.png" alt="Image of a Bug tracker project">
            </div>
            <div class="card-text">
              <h3 class="card-heading">Bug Tracker</h3>
              <p>
                Web application to track projects during their development cycle. For user to use this app, an account has to be created for him. 
                After that user can login, create and edit tickets, post comments on projects he was assigned to. 
              </p>
              <div class="card-buttons">
                <a href="https://bug-tracker-webapp.herokuapp.com/users/login" class="card-button" target="_blank"><span class="no-wrap">Live version</span></a>
                <a href="https://github.com/Trebroon/bug-tracker" class="card-button" target="_blank"><span class="no-wrap"></span><i class="bi bi-github" aria-label="git-hub"></i> Git-Hub</span></a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-img">
              <img src="/imgs/projects/ping-pong.png" alt="Image of a project">
            </div>
            <div class="card-text">
              <h3 class="card-heading">Ping Pong Game</h3>
              <p>
                Simple game made with Python using Pygame libary you can play with your friends. Game keeps track of score for each player. If one of the players had enough 
                you can simply restart by pressing "R" button. Game also has some cool sound effects!   
              </p>
              <div class="card-buttons">
                <a href="https://github.com/Trebroon/ping-pong-game" class="card-button" target="_blank"><i class="bi bi-github" aria-label="git-hub"></i> Git-Hub</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
