                Calculator made in Python using graphical interface libary Tkinter.   
              </p>
              <div class="card-buttons">
                <a href="https://github.com/Trebroon/ping-pong-game" class="card-button" target="_blank"><i class="bi bi-github" aria-label="git-hub"></i> Git-Hub</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
